Name: Sperm Runner

There is 2d and 3d minigames. Playing enough long player achieve some steam achievements. Play games with mouse and/or keyboard Features: - 4 minigames - wormsperm player character - intensive gameplay - damageable objects like poop enemy, herpes enemy and chlamydia enemy - simplistic menu - low poly adulth themed objects like poop and viruses
